data.description:
Well, this is certainly a show piece of a home! AND BONUS TO YOU...with acceptable offer THE OWNER WILL DEED LOT NEXT DOOR WITH SALE OF PROPERTY!  APPROX $20,000 - $25,000 ''LAGNIAPPE'' (A GIFT FROM SELLER!)!!!   

From the moment you walk in the front door of this home you feel such a bright, warm feeling of being WELCOMED, of being HOME! You will see it has been loved and well cared for throughout its life. Once inside you will find 2 large living spaces to enjoy, one space with a wood burning fireplace as you enter the front door; the other is in back of the home near patio, back entrance, yard and carport. This room has many options...a large playroom/game room/ entertainment/bonus den area and so much more!  The kitchen is large with plenty of counter space and room for you and all your guests!  You can dine at the bar area, join the cook with a glass of wine or enjoy family dining in the large bay windowed nook.  The rooms in this home are all PLENTY ample in size (and this includes primary and guest bedrooms, closets, laundry room, pantry, etc...). This floor plan and space is perfect for any family. Don't wait to drop by this one.  It is a must SEE on your list!
